      "message": "Nope! This is NOT pure FYI.\n\nThis is tracking items which were:\n  * leased out to somewhere\n  * dropped (due to a DropOldestBatch FullBehavior)\n  * not yet ACK\u0027d/NACK\u0027d (!! this is the important bit)\n\nIn particular, this could manifest as work items which are currently leased out to a goroutine which is working them. The dispatcher needs to account for these to know that there are still workers out doing stuff.\n\nI\u0027m updating the comment in a subsequent CL so we don\u0027t forget...",
